snippet.title: The Fate Of Baldr - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Ananki games are excited to reveal the cinematic trailer for our upcoming title "The Fate of Baldr", an action tower defense game mixing sci-fi and Norse mythology. 

Subscribe to get more updates!

Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1601630/The_Fate_of_Baldr/

A great many thanks to the fantastic animators at https://brikk.se/ for creating the video!

Music: 
"A Warriors Sorrow" & "The Sea Wolves" by Ivan Duch (https://ivanduch.com)
